The Arab flags usually include the color [[green]], which is a symbol of [[Islam]] as well as an emblem of purity, fertility and peace. Common colors in Arab flags are [[Pan-Arab Colors|red, black, white and green]] ([[Pan-Arab colors]]); common symbols include [[Star (polygon)|stars]], [[crescent]]s and the ''[[Shahada]]''.
