{{Infobox recurring event | name =Sarajevo Street Art Festival | native_name = Festival ulične umjetnosti Sarajevo | native_name_lang = | logo = | logo_alt = | logo_caption = | logo_size = | image = File:Sarajevo.street.art.festival.jpg | image_size = | alt = | caption = | status = active | genre = [[Art festival]] | date = <!-- {{start date|YYYY|mm|dd}} "dates=" also works, but do not use both --> | begins = <!-- {{start date|YYYY|mm|dd}} --> | ends = <!-- {{end date|YYYY|mm|dd}} --> | frequency = <!-- Weekly, Monthly, Quarterly, Semi-annually, Annually, Bi-annually, 2nd Tuesday of November, etc. --> | venue = | location = Sarajevo | coordinates = <!-- {{coord|LAT|LON|type:event|display=inline,title}} --> | country = Bosnia and Herzegovina | years_active = 2015 - present | first = <!-- {{start date|YYYY|mm|dd}} "founded=" and "established=" also work --> | founder_name = <!-- or | founders = --> | last = <!-- Date of most recent event; if the event will not be held again, use {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD|df=y}} --> | prev = | next = | participants = | attendance = | capacity = | area = | budget = | activity = | leader_name = | patron = | organised = <!-- "organized=" also works --> | filing = | people = | member = | sponsor = <!-- | or sponsors = --> | website = {{URL|http://www.fuu.ba/}} | footnotes = }} The '''Sarajevo Street Art Festival''' ({{lang-bs|Festival ulične umjetnosti Sarajevo / Фестивал уличне умјетности Сарајево}}) is an annual [[street art]] [[festival]] held in [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.calvertjournal.com/news/show/4723/first-sarajevo-street-art-festival-this-weekend|title=Sarajevo Street Art Festival this weekend|publisher=calvertjournal.com}}</ref> It is held in July of every year and lasts for three days. Each year's edition is made up of numerous street performances, the creation of a new street art quarter in the city, concerts, the painting of large murals and the showcasing of other creative art forms. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2017-07/09/c_136430366.htm|title=Feature: Vibrant Sarajevo with ongoing street art festival|publisher=xinhuanet.com}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://balkans.aljazeera.net/vijesti/sarajevski-street-art-galerija-na-otvorenom|title=Sarajevski street art – galerija na otvorenom|publisher=Al Jazeera Balkans}}</ref> The final day of the festival is dedicated to children and entails stage music, theatrical and gymnastics workshops, jugglers and street magicians. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://visitsarajevo.ba/2017/07/street-art-festival-your-city-your-art/?lang=en|title=Street Art Festival: Your city, your art!|publisher=visitsarajevo.ba}}</ref>
